query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sd_audience_targeting (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  ad_group_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  audience_type ENUM('views', 'purchases', 'similar_products', 'categories', 'audiences') NOT NULL,
  audience_id VARCHAR(100),
  audience_name VARCHAR(255),
  lookback_window INT COMMENT 'Days for remarketing',
  bid DECIMAL(10, 2),
  targeting_status ENUM('enabled', 'paused') DEFAULT 'enabled',
  impressions INT DEFAULT 0,
  clicks INT DEFAULT 0,
  cost DECIMAL(10, 2) DEFAULT 0,
  sales DECIMAL(10, 2) DEFAULT 0,
  orders INT DEFAULT 0,
  acos DECIMAL(10, 4),
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX idx_campaign (campaign_id),
  INDEX idx_audience_type (audience_type)
);
